Package com.ibm.di.UpdateInstaller

Provides classes for the Security Verify Directory Integrator installer.

    AMCInstalledComponent
    Represents an AMC component.
    ASCIIFileUpdate
    Allows modification of ASCII files.

    Allows wrapper scripts to see if the Update Installer is being updated by a fix or rolled back.
